{"tid":134531,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"絲入 今日終於去左MM 學生75折","createTime":"2017-02-25T14:19:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-26T02:59:55.000Z","uid":31454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d634d684a69f0c0be580960315b85b01a2669195","tid":134531,"uid":31454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T14:19:35.000Z","msg":"聽絲打講左咁耐 <br />\n今日終於去左mm 買bra <br />\n感覺姨姨真係好細心 <br />\n會入黎教你應該點戴bra <br />\n點撥點洗 樣樣都覺得好好 <br />\n去過蔡太 覺得同蔡太真係好大分別<br />\n價錢好似差唔多 但今日學生有75折 <br />\n感覺平左好多 買左3個試下 <br />\n如果舒服想買多3個 <br />\n臨走佢叫我2星期到再去「覆疹」<br />\n希望會有用啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0017504f124fafc1572e745288bd034589031eb2","tid":134531,"uid":9185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T14:24:48.000Z","msg":"男人老狗都戴bra,肥仔波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb6b9d8e64e3202eab0cce0e7bb8cca0711284dd","tid":134531,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T14:27:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d41fa7419826a259669d13070ae879d6b042fb2e","tid":134531,"uid":31454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T14:44:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>男人老狗都戴bra,肥仔波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你想戴都可以 千奇唔好灰心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20e1a0407c2447175cb48e265c55cee306978c23","tid":134531,"uid":31454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T14:45:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://www.zonaeuropa.com/20100118_01.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.zonaeuropa.com%2F20100118_01.jpg&d=FZf2Eq7oNugCj0cVmX%2F%2FqS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=61bd70c5\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.zonaeuropa.com/20100118_01.jpg</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.zonaeuropa.com/20100118_02.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.zonaeuropa